original: Face off a different take on the field of strife!
translation: 在这片充满冲突的土地上面对又一场不同的战斗!

original: Face off against special Arcade Machines that can tune in to different jams and spawn different zombies!
translation: 面对特殊的街机, 它可以在不同的音乐中制造不同的僵尸!

original: Face one of the hardest conveyor levels that have ever been made!
translation: 面对迄今为止最难的传送带关卡之一!

original: Fire and ice clashes! Can you take advantage of the situation?
translation: 冰与火的碰撞! 你能好好利用吗?

original: Foil another one of Zomboss's devious challenges in this snow-ridden battlefield!
translation: 在这个白雪覆盖的战场上, 在僵王博士另一个狡猾的挑战中让他挫败!

original: Fun little puzzle ahead! Move those Troglobites around to complete it!
translation: 有趣的小谜题! 移动推冰僵尸来解密!

original: Gaze into the future of technology and figure out a way to deal with a field full of runes!
translation: 展望未来的科技, 找出解决充满符文的领域的方法!

original: Get ready for some interesting challenges based off of our newest resident!
translation: 准备好面对我们最新居民的趣味挑战吧!

original: Get to know our resident berry in the heart of the jungle!
translation: 来了解一下丛林中心的常驻浆果吧!

original: Go back in time once more to face the calamari onslaught of the past!
translation: 再次回到过去, 面对过去的乌贼的猛攻!

original: Go back to the beginning with this brand new epic quest!
translation: 通过这个全新的史诗任务回到起点!

original: Go on a journey with the latest addition to the garden: mini plants! Starting with Mini Pea!
translation: 带着花园的最新成员: 迷你植物来一场旅行吧! 从迷你豌豆开始!

original: Go on yet another rescue mission as you uncover a secret in the desert... at night!
translation: 你在沙漠之夜中发现了一个... 秘密, 前往另一项解救任务吧!

original: Gotta be tough to stand against the primal! Complete 8-10!
translation: 跟原始人对抗一定要强硬! 通关8-10!

original: Gotta be tough to stand against the primal! Complete 8-10X!
translation: 跟原始人对抗一定要强硬! 通关8-10X!

original: Gravestones are blocking your path! Plan your defense around them!
translation: 墓碑挡住了你的去路! 围绕它们制定防御计划!

original: Gravestones inbound! Bounce on them for maximum bounciness!
translation: 墓碑进场了! 在它们之间弹跳以获得最多的连击!

original: Harness the power of Crystall-shroom as she makes her debut!
translation: 冰晶菇首次亮相! 好好利用她的力量吧!

original: Head back to the origin of the party as we crash the beach!
translation: 我们冲到海滩上, 回到派对的起源!

original: Hidden underneath the golden exterior lies something sinister... watch out!
translation: 在金色的外表下隐藏着邪恶的东西... 小心!

original: Hold down your defense with all kind of exotic leaves!
translation: 用各种奇异的叶子来控制你的防御!

original: Hold on to your pirate hat - Spring Bean's up to bat those zombies back!
translation: 拿好你的海盗帽 - 弹簧豆要把那些僵尸弹飞了!

original: How are you going to hit zombies threatening two blocked lanes? Electric Blueberry to the rescue!
translation: 你要怎么对付威胁两条被阻挡的道路的僵尸? 电击蓝莓来拯救你!

original: I want to play a game.
translation: 我想玩一个游戏.

original: Iceberg ahead! Do not crash! Complete 5-10!
translation: 前方有冰山! 不要撞上了! 通关5-10!

original: Iceberg ahead! Do not crash! Complete 5-10X!
translation: 前方有冰山! 不要撞上了! 通关5-10X!

original: I'm running outta names at this point, so sorry. Welcome to hell anyway!
translation: 这次我想不出什么名字了, 抱歉. 总之欢迎来到地狱!

original: Join us on a bowling party across time and space!
translation: 加入我们跨越时空的保龄球派对吧!

original: Learn how to harness the power of ice as Ice-shroom makes his first debut!
translation: 寒冰菇首次亮相! 学习如何利用冰的力量吧!

original: Let's conquer the power of sand! Complete 11-10!
translation: 让我们征服沙子的力量吧! 通关11-10!

original: Lots of iceblocks everywhere! Can you handle the frozen heat?
translation: 到处都是冰块! 你能忍受被冰封的高温吗?

original: Make use of iceblocks these mini plants are trapped in and fight back with Hot Potato's scalding damage!
translation: 好好利用这些包含迷你植物的冰块, 用热土豆的烫伤伤害反击!

original: Making sun during the night won't be an easy feat... with all the sun producers gone!
translation: 在夜间生产阳光并不是一件容易的事情... 而且所有的太阳生产者都消失了!

original: Master the deep jungle! Complete 12-10!
translation: 征服丛林深处! 通关12-10!

original: Meet and greet a familiar face... or is it?
translation: 迎接一个熟悉的面孔... 真的是这样吗?

original: Meet the last of the mini plants, and also the most explosive one yet!
translation: 迎接最后一株迷你植物, 也是最具爆炸性的一个!

original: Night 3 of the battle! Now we're getting serious!
translation: 大战的第三夜! 现在我们可是认真的!

original: Night has fallen upon the battlefield! Make use of the given headstart!
translation: 夜幕降临在战场上! 好好利用开局给予的东西吧!

original: Now we set sail! Complete 4-10!
translation: 现在我们起航了! 通关4-10!

original: Now we set sail! Complete 4-10X!
translation: 现在我们起航了! 通关4-10X!

original: One last hurrah! Will you prevail, or will you become extinct?
translation: 千钧一发之际! 你将会获胜, 还是会灭绝?

original: Only one Moonflower left! How will the shadow family thrive?
translation: 只剩最后一株月光花了! 暗影家族将如何茁壮成长?

original: Out-perform them all in the ultimate show! Complete 20-10!
translation: 在最终的表演中超越他们! 通关20-10!

original: Overgrown zombies are approaching! Can you Lock and Load your way out of this?
translation: 长得过大的僵尸正在逼近! 你能把这事搞定吗?

original: Participate in an intense training to get to know your resident citrus!
translation: 参加一个高强度的培训来了解你的香橼!

original: Plan and plant your defense to stand against the danger of the night!
translation: 计划和种植你的防御, 以抵御夜晚的危险!

original: Play around with Hypno-shroom in a different setting!
translation: 在不同的场合中使用魅惑菇吧!

original: Plentiful back attacks incoming! Use Strawbursts' self-explosion to your advantage!
translation: 大量的背部攻击来了! 利用爆浆草莓的自我爆炸对你有利!

original: Portal mayhem! Hold down the fort with the power of Spring Bean!
translation: 传送门大混乱! 用弹簧豆的力量坚守堡垒!

original: Portals and tents and birds from hell, oh my! Will you prevail?
translation: 传送门, 帐篷, 还有来自地狱的鸟, 天啊! 你会赢吗?

original: Potent Plant Food effects from Magnifying Grass and Mini Potato Mine might just save you from this futuristic nightmare!
translation: 棱镜草和迷你土豆地雷的强大叶绿素效果可能会把你从这个未来的噩梦中拯救出来!

original: Protect our beloved bean from one last undead attack!
translation: 保护我们心爱的豆子免遭最后一波活死人的攻击!

original: Protect our beloved grunting nuts before they are devoured!
translation: 在我们心爱的坚果被吃掉之前, 保护他们吧!

original: Protect our piercing friends against an unrelenting zombie horde!
translation: 保护我们穿透的朋友们不受无情的僵尸群的伤害!

original: Protect the flower line from an attack from both directions!
translation: 保护花坛免受来自两个方向的攻击!

original: Protect the flower line from being brutally trampled by those brutal zombies!
translation: 保护花坛不被那些残忍的僵尸残酷践踏!

original: Protect the Strawbursts against a plethora of dangerous long-ranged zombies!
translation: 保护爆浆草莓对抗过多的危险远程僵尸!

original: Protect these endangered Electric Blueberries against a swarm of big bad Gargantuars!
translation: 保护这些濒危的电击蓝莓免受一群又大又坏的巨人的攻击!

original: Protect these plasma shooters from a hoarde of HUGE zombies!
translation: 从一只巨大的僵尸大军手中保护这些等离子射手!

original: Put your skills to the test against yet another chilling conveyor level!
translation: 在另一个令人毛骨悚然的传送带关卡中测试你的技能吧!

original: Reclaim the desert! Complete 21-10!
translation: 收复沙漠! 完成21-10!

translation: 成为中世纪村庄的统治者! 通关3-10!

original: Shiver me timber, the sea will be ours! Complete 14-10!
translation: 想吓唬我? 大海将是我们的! 通关14-10!

original: Show'em the sharpest shooter's skills! Complete 6-10!
translation: 让他们见识见识最厉害的射手技术! 通关6-10!

translation: 让他们见识见识最厉害的射手技术! 通关6-10X!

original: Solve a fiendish puzzle, featuring the plant himself!
translation: 解开一个聚焦植物本身的恶魔般的谜题!

original: Space saving is important when it comes to these mini plants - especially on tidal waves!
translation: 当涉及到这些迷你植物时, 节省空间是很重要的 - 尤其是在潮汐上!

original: Spread the poison to everyone while stalling to avoid meeting your demise!
translation: 在拖延时间以避免死亡的同时, 将毒到处传播!

original: Start off this Epic Quest with a battle in the Wild West!
translation: 用一场在狂野西部的战斗开始这个史诗任务!

original: Surf's up! Time to \ hang ten\ ! Complete 17-10!

original: Survive against an army of Knights using the bare minimum!
translation: 用最少的资源对抗骑士军团!

original: Take back the treasured relics! Complete 22-10!
translation: 把珍贵的文物拿回来! 通关22-10!

original: Take on an icy onslaught with only a handful of plants and limited sun supply!

original: Take part in an epic attempt to recover a rare mushroom plant!

original: The future for these endangered Beans are uncertain, as portals invade the lawn once more! Protect them!
